data.description: *BACK ON THE MARKET!* Step into the welcoming embrace of this beautiful, large 6-bedroom, 4-bathroom home nestled in a peaceful, sought-after neighborhood. Here, you'll find a haven that offers space and comfort for everyone in your family. All appliances included! The heart of this house is its inviting kitchen with its open layout connecting to the dining area and living room, you'll enjoy taking part in every gathering. The spacious backyard is ready for outdoor activities and playtime. Great schools and a friendly community, making this not just a house, but the perfect home to create lasting memories. Don't let this spacious gem slip away  reach out today to make it your own! Buyer to verify all measurements and details. Home is sold as-is.
